$PAR SOLUTION $PAR

The restrictions
\( $theta0 \leq\theta\le $theta1 \quad $phi0\le\phi\leq $phi1 \) :
correspond to \{ $surf1->correct_ans() \}.
$BR$BR
The restrictions
\( $theta2 \leq\theta\le $theta3 \quad $phi2\le\phi\leq $phi3 \) :
correspond to \{ $surf2->correct_ans() \}. 

END_SOLUTION
